name: William Prebble
description:
My name is William, I’m 43 years old widower, I’m an outgoing type of person who is
completely laid back and easy going. I’m down to earth with a sense of humor, easy to approach and I easily make friends too. I’m interested in meeting like minded folks cuz like attract likes. I am an open minded person who has interest in learning new languages, cultures, foods and new ways of life. Please write me and let us get to know each other.
I am looking for someone that I can get lost in conversation with just as easily as we can share one of those moments of comfortable silence in each others arms. I love to laugh and joke around. My job is awesome, but I know when I come home that this is where my priorities and true happiness are.
